        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "four numbers off the list. Repeat with the three smallest remaining numbers 4, 5, 7 and their sum 16. Continue in this way, crossing off the three smallest remaining numbers and their sum, and consider the sequence of sums produced: 6, 16, 27, 36, . ... Prove or disprove that there is some number in the sequence whose base 10 representation ends with 2015.",
